title: [Elliania's Outfitting]
description: Enclosed by painted emerald green walls, the shop features a small potted boxwood shrub in the center of its glossy tanik floor.  A snarling war griffin painting hangs under the nightscape ceiling.  Right near the front is a wide faenor-trimmed table and a large oak table.

Beneath a painted nightscape ceiling, a snarling war griffin painting hangs on one of the painted emerald green walls.  A wide faenor-trimmed table and a large oak table sit in opposite corners while a small potted boxwood shrub rests on a wide-plank glossy tanik floor.
